Device description to build Alcatel OT993D Recovery Image

To build
1) Copy local_manifest.xml to .repo/
2) do "repo sync" from source root
3) . build/envsetup.sh
4) lunch full_OT993D-eng
5) make recoveryimage -j8

Links:
 - Modified CWM - https://github.com/samm-git/android_bootable_recovery
 - Kernel - https://github.com/samm-git/alcatel_ot993D_kernel

